						<summary>

						<p>On a stone set up on the road leading to the river.</p>						

						<p>The record in late Brāhmī characters may be assigned on palaeographical grounds to c. third century A.D.</p>						

						<p>This fragmentary inscription mentions a certain <hi rend="italic">Sanakasa.</hi> Other details are not clear.</p>						

